hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: What company are you calling from? www.apexpharma.com.my I’ve been on the other side of the coin, too – when I first started out in comedy, I had a few dalliances of varying lengths (don’t be dirty) with (ahem) my ‘colleagues’. An occupational hazard of being a comedian’s other half is that your relationship may well become the subject of your beloved’s act. Indeed, sometimes the act reveals more than any deep and meaningful chat ever could, and there were times when I would actually go along to my former boyfriends’ gigs simply in order to find out what was going on in our relationship. Of course, it was embarrassing sometimes, and certainly I’d have preferred to find out in private that things weren’t going so well for us, but if it has to happen at a grungy stand-up club in Liverpool whilst surrounded by 300 guffawing strangers, then I guess it’s better than nothing – at least you know where you stand.
